title: Thales Payshield Info 
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/Payshield
license: Propertary
distribution: Propertary
description:
 This check always gives back OK state and it's primary use is to report some important payshield hsm informations via check_mk

 The Output of check plugin provides: 

 - Payshield Info: {SERIALNUMBER}

 Long output of check plugin provides 

 - System Serial Number: {SERIALNUMBER}

 - Version Software Base Release: {VERSION}

 - Version Software Revision: {REEVISION}

 - Version Software Build Number: {BUILDNUMBER}

 - Version Software HSM Core API Version: {APIVERISON}

 - Licensing Performance Model: {PERFORMANCELIMIT}

 - Licensing Optional License Count: {LICENSESCOUNT}

 - Licensing Optional Licenses List: {LISTOFALLLICENSES}

 - Licensing Crypto Algorithm Count: {CRYPTOALGORITHMCOUNT}

 - Licensing Crypto Algorithm List: {LISTOFCRYPTOALGORITHM}

 - Enabled Host Commands Count: {COMMANDCOUNT}

 - Enabled Host Commands List: {LISTOFENABLEDCOMMANDS}

 - Settings PCI Compliant: {PCICOMPLIANCE}


inventory:
 This check creates "Payshield Info" check if the Thales-ENTERPRISE SNMP OID is found

